Bobby Ray DEVERS, Applicant-Appellant,
v.
STATE of Iowa, Respondent-Appellee. No. 18-0121 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 23, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Applicant appeals the district court's summary dismissal of his fourth postconviction-relief action. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
